column2: "I've had enough. This place is not suited for an engagement."
"It seems there will be a more appropriate place to do battle with you."
"This place is boorish. I can't take any satisfaction in fighting you here."
"Give him back... Give Master Gettemhart back...."
"Hm, you were there to help unseal me, and now you want my host back. Make up your mind."
"But I was able to come into being because of your thoughtless actions, so I must thank you for that."
"Tell me, worthless creature, what is your name?"
"Shina, if you want to reclaim his existence, then crush me with those tiny arms of yours."
"That is what this host wishes of you."
